The paper also deals with similarity selection, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR), suggesting that it could belong to the cs.IR sub-category. The paper utilizes regression models and feature extraction, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (AI), suggesting that it could belong to the cs.AI sub-category.
